<div tiddler="RicohInnovations" modifier="JeremyRuston" modified="200609291100" created="200609271202" tags="">RicohInnovations sees TiddlyWiki as a key component in creating service innovations rapidly and at low cost. For example, some teachers and students have found TiddlyWiki notebooks to be a better way of sharing course notes and other information.\n\nRicohInnovations has supported work on the TiddlyWiki core code to facilitate these kinds of experiments in [[improving services|http://www.rii.ricoh.com/pres_letter.html]].</div>